<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>feign death does not make you invinsable, it meerly enables you to fake death to where your mob will think your dead and walk away. this spell can be found in neriak at the necro/sk guild. also, if attack is on, it can make the spell not work as well, also, very important, if you find this spell does not work, try practicing in what ever it is, like alteration, conjuration, etc. that will help greatly. this is a great spell, its saved my ass from 20 froglocks b4 that were on my ass when my invis wore off in gukk, and i was bound in south karana, keep it memed, its a life saver, just make sure you are around 80 in its skill. good hunting to yo all  </font></td></tr></table>
