<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I used this a couple of nights ago in perma when my party all died to a large train my pet killed the one i had cast my dots on so i figured i was safe and tried to feign to avoid zoning and losing my pet. for the record everything in the room still aggroed on me.</font></td></tr></table>
